snippet.title: Astria Ascending | Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing Astria Ascending, a J-RPG developed by Artisan Studios, and planned for release in 2021 on Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and Xbox Game Pass.
Visit astria-ascending.com for more information.
